              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12915388726157210518">Originally read as assigned in undergrad, but upon re-reading realized that the <i>Lais</i> are much subtler than I had allotted time to appreciate. Good stories of courtly romance and observations about love - as experienced, pursued, and idealized by that particularly chivalric wedge of medieval society.</span>

