        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer34254109" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12027707779526055754">Marie took over my dissertation (and my life) for several months. Even after dissertation (AD) I&apos;m able to love her! Each lai is a gem. She was post-modern in the Middle Ages. Her voice rings clear and true. Her stories are magical. </span>
